text: Kalisho Devi A lot of care has to be taken while making and maintaining the murabba. The container in which the murabba is kept should be washed with boiled water and exposed to sunlight or dry in the microwave. it should not contain any kind of moisture or dirt, the murabba should be taken out with a clean washed spoon, Don't put your hand in it. Just like pickle, murabba has to be taken care .
